item.title: JBrowser
item.author: open2idos@gmail.com (openeidos)
item.description: Welcome to JBrowser github website. The JBrowser is a browser for developers. The JBrowser is the addition of DataBase to the function of a regular browser. In addition, the sql language can be used during search. and information can be inquired and stored by building a simple DB. Thank you for finding it.
